                                           "es suborganización de manera transitiva de"@es ,
                                           "sotto-Organization transitiva"@it ,
                                           "sous-Organization transitive de"@fr ,
                                           "transitive sub-organization"@en .


###  http://www.w3.org/ns/org#unitOf
org:unitOf rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
